---
const siteName = "小庭小世界";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>关于我 | {siteName}</title>
  
  <style is:raw>
* {
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: SimSun, "宋体", sans-serif !important;
  background: #FFF0F6;
  background-image: radial-gradient(pink 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 20px 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
}

nav {
  width: 92%;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 10px auto;
  border: 2px solid #F4A7C1;
  background: #FFF;
  padding: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 6px;
}
.nav-links a {
  color: #C45A81;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 14px;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  border: 1px solid #F4A7C1;
  background: #FFE6F0;
  font-family: SimSun, "宋体" !important;
}
.nav-links a:hover {
  background: #F4A7C1;
  color: #FFF;
}
.nav-links a.active {
  background: #F4A7C1;
  color: #FFF;
  font-weight: normal;
}

.page {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 0 1rem;
}
.page h1 {
  color: #e64980;
  font-size: 20px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-family: SimSun, "宋体";
}

/* ========== 超小头像 48x48px ========== */
.my-photo {
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto 12px;
  width: 48px;     /* 超小宽度 */
  height: 48px;    /* 超小高度 */
  object-fit: cover;
  border: 1px solid #F4A7C1;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.about-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #C45A81;
  padding: 10px;
}
.about-card p {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.about-card h3 {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #e64980;
  margin: 12px 0 6px;
  font-family: SimSun, "宋体";
}
.about-card ul {
  margin-left: 20px;
}
.about-card li {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin: 30px 0;
  color: #999;
  font-size: 12px;
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/">首页</a>
    <a href="/diary">小日记</a>
    <a href="/review">音影书评</a>
    <a href="/guestbook">留言板</a>
    <a href="/ask">提问箱</a>
    <a href="/postcard">明信片</a>
    <a href="/about" class="active">关于我</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="page">
  <h1>✨ 关于我</h1>

  <!-- 迷你小头像 -->
  <img src="/assets/aboutme.jpg" alt="小庭" class="my-photo">

  <div class="about-card">
    <p>你好呀！我是小庭，这里是我的世界～</p>
    
    <h3>💡 关于这个网站</h3>
    <p>生活无聊产物，感谢豆包、deepseek的鼎力支持，感谢大哥！</p>
    <p>INFP低精力爱幻想，最近在找寻小时候的味道</p>

    
    <h3>🎈 我的小爱好</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>卢广仲超级粉丝</li>
      <li>喜欢明信片，追求片票戳终极大和谐的非极限实寄爱好者</li>
      <li>会手写日记，记录生活里的大幸福大烦恼</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>📮 联系方式</h3>
    <p>邮箱：yuji200s@126.com </p>
    <p>如果你想和我聊天，可以去「留言板」或「提问箱」给我留言～虽然还没有做好（buhaoyisi</p>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  © 2026 {siteName} | 小庭的小世界 哈哈哈欢迎你来看小庭啊
</footer>
</body>
</html>